CREAMY SOUP WITH SALMON

00:00:11.159 --> 00:00:14.129
Hello!

00:00:14.129 --> 00:00:20.400
I will cook a creamy soup with salmon. We need:

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:33.690
300 g salmon filet, 150 g carrots, 500 g potatoes, 2 onions, 300 g tomatoes, green-stuff, 1 l water, 500 ml cream and salt.

00:00:33.690 --> 00:00:43.150
Onions and carrots cut into straws.

00:00:43.150 --> 00:01:00.230
First into thin strips, then into straws.

00:01:01.670 --> 00:01:11.400
In a preheated pan pour a little vegetable oil.

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:21.530
Fry the carrots over medium heat.

00:01:21.530 --> 00:01:28.530
Cut the onion into thin strips, or you can simply chop.

00:01:55.310 --> 00:02:03.320
Stir and fry until lightly golden brown onions.

00:02:03.320 --> 00:02:09.340
We will remove skins from tomatoes.

00:02:09.340 --> 00:02:20.049
To do this, throw them in boiling water for a couple of minutes.

00:02:20.049 --> 00:02:35.249
We took out the tomatoes.

00:02:40.509 --> 00:02:57.969
Remove the skins from the tomatoes and cut into small cubes.

00:03:04.269 --> 00:03:15.000
Add the tomatoes to the pan and fry for 5 minutes.

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:28.209
Cut the potatoes into cubes.

00:03:33.369 --> 00:03:40.369
Cut fish into cubes.

00:03:43.569 --> 00:04:04.089
Put the potatoes in a pan, fish - on the top.

00:04:04.089 --> 00:04:09.189
Put over low heat, cover with a lid and wait for thermocontrol indicator will be in the middle of green section.

00:04:09.189 --> 00:04:16.150
Arrow has reached the middle of the green section. You can open the lid.

00:04:16.150 --> 00:04:33.610
Add water, stir and salt.

00:04:33.610 --> 00:04:40.610
Increase the heat and heated up to the boiling point.

00:04:41.779 --> 00:04:50.360
Soup to boil. Add the cream.

00:04:55.139 --> 00:05:04.430
Stir and heated to the boiling point. We taste for quantity salt.

00:05:04.430 --> 00:05:11.430
Heat up and boil for 5 minutes.

00:05:14.089 --> 00:05:24.080
The result is tender, flavorful and hearty soup.

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:32.069
Can be sprinkled with fresh greens on top.

00:05:32.069 --> 00:05:35.029
Bon appetit!

